{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You say to the [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[HEBREW] means two meaning, two meanings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It means what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It also means they wanted to cool you, [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted to chill you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wanted to get off-- to take away-- away your, your strength and your spirit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a, it is-- you can't help it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Life goes on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, when you find yourself, that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, in between, when I-- from there, they-- I had to go to-- they took us to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was a-- from [POLISH] to Auschwitz, it was a real-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I wouldn't say experience.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was a-- the most, the next to hell or even more than that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they put us all in trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and we were traveling through Prague in open boxcars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were so squeezed that we could not turn even.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, the only place we could find a relief was-- because a lot of people in these boxcars, they just perished, they died.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So what we did is we just put them down on the side, and we sat on them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the only place we could-- This was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When we left [POLISH] and we came to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So-- and we traveled probably about at least two days in [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 40 degrees, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cold weather.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Without food, without anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The only what-- the only thing you could get is when the train stopped, we jumped down to get a little hot water from the locomotive, with the steam.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was shooting out, a little hot water.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
